text: Sidensjö IK is a sports club in Sidensjö in Sweden. The club was established in 1921. It runs soccer, track and field athletics, gymnastics, orienteering and skiing. The women's soccer team played five seasons in the Swedish top division between 1978-1986. ==References== ==Other websites== *Soccer *Orienteering Category:1921 establishments in Sweden Category:Swedish football clubs Category:Athletics clubs in Sweden Category:Gymnastics Category:Ski clubs in Sweden
